# This directory holds rollback artifacts produced by ./deploy.sh.
# Each deploy writes one zip here BEFORE pushing new code to AWS, so
# the prior production state is always one command away from restore.
#
# Naming: <function>-<utc-timestamp>-<sha8>.zip
#   sha8 = first 8 chars of the deployed CodeSha256 the backup captured.
#
# *.zip is gitignored. The directory itself is tracked via this .gitkeep
# so a fresh checkout has the directory ready (deploy.sh creates it
# defensively too).
#
# See ROLLBACK.md for how to use these.
